// Fake tracking
//
// Until the 'trak' table support becomes available in CoreText,
// tracking is imitated as kerning across the whole stream.
// Note the space is not tracked before a word; Safari will ignore it anyway.

Type Contextual
Orientation H

Spc	space

		EOT	OOB	DEL	EOL	Spc
StartText	1	2	1	1	3
StartLine	1	2	1	1	3
Space		1	1	1	1	3

	GoTo		Push?		Advance?	KernList
1	StartText	no		yes		none
2	StartText	yes		yes		Track
3	Space		yes		yes		Track

